                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910914-47-off294 t17910914-47-cd295"></join> last, two wether sheep, value 50 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17910914-47-victim479" type="victimName">
                  Criss 
                  Pooley
               <interp inst="t17910914-47-victim479" type="surname" value="Pooley"></interp>
