               <p>I drove Mr. Harwood's sheep to the field from Clerkenwell, I took them to Battle-bridge; I never saw the sheep till I came to Clerkenwell-green.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17910914-47-person494">
                  CHARLES
                   PURDEY
               <interp inst="t17910914-47-person494" type="surname" value="PURDEY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17910914-47-person494" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>
